Mavericks

https://nplab.fh-muenster.de/groups/wiki/wiki/bf935/SCTP_on_Mavericks.html

Mountain Lion

https://nplab.fh-muenster.de/groups/wiki/wiki/f366c/SCTP_on_Mountain_Lion.html

Windows

The SCTP driver for Windows was downloaded from
http://www.bluestop.org/SctpDrv. Please install the package.
